SELECT "error".sum::decimal / "all".sum
FROM
    (SELECT sum(count) as sum from jmeter_metrics.sample_metric
     WHERE
         timestamp BETWEEN '2024-08-26T12:34:30.611Z' AND '2024-08-26T13:36:30.611Z' AND
             (-9999 in ('18268') OR test_id in ('18268')) AND
             ('%%all%%' in ('%%all%%') OR location IN ('%%all%%')) AND
             not is_transaction) as "all",
    (SELECT sum(count) as sum from jmeter_metrics.sample_error_metric
     WHERE
         timestamp BETWEEN '2024-08-26T12:34:30.611Z' AND '2024-08-26T13:36:30.611Z' AND
             (-9999 in ('18268') OR test_id in ('18268')) AND
             ('%%all%%' in ('%%all%%') OR location IN ('%%all%%')) AND
             not is_transaction) as "error";
